lyrics:
[verse]
In the realm of ecstasy, the beats collide
The rhythm takes hold, my spirit comes alive
Unleashing energy, as I dance through the night
Techno pulses, igniting my inner light

[chorus]
Drog, techno, brocoli, let's embrace the blend
In this wild fusion, our senses transcend
A kaleidoscope of sounds, we stand tall
Dancing to the beat, surrendering to the call
